[SN]TITLE[SN]
Bangor shooting: Man arrested in connection with murder of Colin Horner

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A 28-year-old man has been arrested in connection with the murder of a man in a supermarket car park.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Colin Horner, 35, was shot in front of his three-year-old son at Balloo Link, Bangor, on Sunday afternoon.
Police described his murder as "brutal, senseless and horrendous".
They have previously said that they are investigating a possible link between Mr Horner's murder and a loyalist paramilitary feud.
